    public abstract class ProcessAndResultBase<ProcessParameter,​ResultParameter>
extends ProcessAndResultBoard<ProcessParameter,​ResultParameter>
    A base class for an EBC that CanProcess and SendsResult. The implementation contains the boilerplate code required to implement the interfaces and provides trace logging of action and event invocations.
    Author:
    tilmann
